title: [Maelstrom Bay, Bottom]
description: The sandy bay floor is crisscrossed with the tracks of marine life...crabs, lobsters, sea slugs, bay roaches.  A hazy spray of silt is suspended in the water, carried slowly eastward by the gentle current.  A pair of sea fans, like the ears of an elephant, grows out of the golden sand of the bay floor.
paths: Obvious exits: north, east, southeast, south, southwest, west, northwest, up
